Package: xfce4-quark-weather-plugin
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, xfce4-panel, librsvg2-common, glib-networking
Description: Quark Weather — modern Xfce panel weather plugin
 A glassmorphism-styled weather plugin for the Xfce panel.
 Shows current conditions, hourly forecasts, and 7-day outlook
 using free met.no data — no API key required.
 .
 Features include location search via OpenStreetMap, automatic
 IP-based geolocation, SVG weather icons, and wttr.in fallback.
